description.text: Unique furnished European-style unit for lease inside Village Green! This is a one-of-a-kind split level, 2 bedroom, 1 bath townhouse with a cozy fireplace, a balcony with stunning views, and in-unit laundry available for lease on 8/1/23. Just bring your luggage and toothbrush and enjoy the grand living inside this special place you can call home. Other features include a serene private patio with colorful plants and trees, a 1-car private garage, and 24/7 patrolled security! Come be a part of this mid-century National Historical Landmark where you are surrounded by trees and a park-like setting, and have community events such as live concerts, potlucks, and bird watching tours, among many others. This is a great opportunity to living inside an urban forest close to LAX, Beverly Hills, DTLA, Baldwin Hills, Crenshaw Plaza, and walking & rolling distance to the Metro Expo Line and trendy Downtown Culver City. No pets. Available 8/1/23. Call for private showings!

open_houses.description: Step into this modern, remodeled home in West Adams. Situated near amenities, parks, and cultural hotspots, it offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an elegant open kitchen. Enjoy French Oak flooring, quality fixtures, a luxurious primary suite with a marble bath, and a walk-in closet. An attached two-car garage, security-ready wiring, and high-end appliances add convenience. Outside, a landscaped yard with a patio, an outdoor fireplace, and an avocado tree invite relaxation. Don't miss this lease opportunity in a vibrant, trendy neighborhood. Experience the best of West Adams.

description.text: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of West Adams. This recently remodeled modern residence offers the perfect combination of style, convenience, and comfort. Located in a fantastic neighborhood with easy access to the 10, this home is surrounded by amenities that make daily life a breeze. Nestled in close proximity to some of the best restaurants in the area, a new Whole Foods Market, and Kenneth Hahn Park, you'll have everything you need right at your doorstep. Moreover, this home is located a few doors away from Westside Neighborhood Park, providing a convenient and accessible outdoor space for recreation and leisure. Additionally, across the street, you'll find the Good Earth Community Garden, offering an urban farm right outside your front door. The property is also situated adjacent to the vibrant Culver City Arts District and the newly urbanized Jefferson/La Cienega corridor, ensuring endless opportunities for cultural experiences and entertainment. Step inside and be amazed by the attention to detail and quality craftsmanship evident in every square inch. The home features wide-panel hardwood French Oak flooring throughout, adding warmth and elegance to every room. The open-concept kitchen and living area are both stunning and spacious, featuring beautiful black stone countertops, a white handcrafted tile backsplash, and custom cabinets that exude modern elegance. The high-end designer fixtures and hardware throughout the home showcase the commitment to excellence. This home offers three bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The primary bedroom is a true oasis, boasting French Doors that overlook and open up to the backyard. The primary bath is a luxurious retreat with exquisite marble countertops, a marble floor, and marble shower walls. The primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet, providing ample storage space. The impeccable landscaping surrounding the property adds to its charm and curb appeal. You'll love spending time outdoors on the patio, perfect for dining under the stars. The large and spacious grass backyard, adorned with a fruit-bearing avocado tree, offers endless possibilities for relaxation and play. It also features a separate sitting area and an outdoor fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for cozy evenings. The home is wired and ready for a security system, ensuring peace of mind. All high-end appliances, including a Frigidaire Professional Stainless Steel Gas Range and Oven, Frigidaire Gallery French door refrigerator, convenient drawer microwave oven, and dishwasher, make daily tasks a joy. With a washer and dryer as well an an attached two-car garage, convenience is at your fingertips. Don't miss the opportunity to lease this incredible property in one of the most desirable and trendy neighborhoods on the West side. Act now and experience the best of West Adams living.

description.text: Beautifully remodeled 3bed/2 bath duplex for rent in the fast-changing West Adams neighborhood. This unit has been fully remodeled and features all brand-new natural wood waterproof vinyl flooring, contemporary bathroom shower/tile, modern kitchen cabinets, and Quartz Kitchen countertops. The bedrooms are well sized offering plenty of closet space with tons of natural light. The unit also offers in unit washer and dryer connections. Landlord pays for water and landscaping while tenant is responsible for all other utilities. description.text: 5263 West Adams is located in the West Adams District, a historical neighborhood central to everything Los Angeles. With most of its buildings aging between 1880 and 1925. Live in this up and coming vibrant community filled with history and opportunity, with an array of local dining and shopping options all the while living in an intimate and modern home. 5263 West Adams is situated on the western end of West Adams Boulevard, between South Fairfax Avenue and South La Brea Avenue, just south of the I-10. The area is well-served by the Expo Line, offering quick access to Culver City, USC and Downtown.

Inside laundry unit is included in a separate area off the kitchen. A spacious living room is perfect for entertaining. 1 car garage and ample guest parking. This is a secure gated environment that is accessed via a security gate that is guarded 24 hours daily. The complex also boasts, a large swimming pool, 2 spas, a tennis court and a banquet/recreation hall. Cameo Woods is the best kept secret on the Westside! Within close proximity to the Expo line station at Jefferson, Whole Foods, Target and the Baldwin Hills stairs.

description.text: Welcome home to this cute, updated 1920s Spanish Casita with beautiful fenced front yard in blossoming West Adams! A fully detached 2 bedroom plus bonus room house with no shared walls and no one above or below, this is the front unit of a small triplex. Adorable arched front atrium porch leads into a main living area featuring plenty of natural light and character elements: a decorative fireplace flanked by built-in storage cabinets and charming arched partitions that reveal an updated kitchen with new stainless steel appliances. Two bedrooms are connected by a Jack & Jill bathroom that has new floor tiles, a new toilet, new mirrored medicine cabinet, new space-saving sink, freshly reglazed bath tub, and new multi-function shower head. Bonus room with additional ensuite three-quarter bathroom features a stackable laundry unit and would make an ideal office, laundry room, yoga room, or possible small third bedroom. Newly installed HVAC unit provides central heat and air conditioning controlled by a Nest thermostat. Enjoy the outdoors in the lush front yard surrounded by bougainvillea, fire stick plant, and passionfruit vines embracing a private perimeter fence. Comes with a single-car garage for parking and/or storage, and an optional second uncovered off-street parking spot. Near West Adams hot spots Highly Likely Cafe, Party Beer Company Brewery, Cento, Alta, Adams Wine Shop, Vicky's All Day, and so much more. Less than 2 miles from the LaCienega Whole Foods Market which just opened last year. Enjoy all this super-central location has to offer!
